			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>As the ghost of your ancestor enters your body, a crimson veil falls before your vision. Your actions become those of the beast within you.</i></p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Encounter</b></p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Standard Action</b><b> &#8226; </b><b>Melee</b> 1</p><p><b>Effect:</b> You shift your speed. </p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Target:</b> Each enemy you move adjacent to while shifting </p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Attack:</b> Strength + 6 vs. AC, Constitution + 6 vs. AC, or Dexterity + 6 vs. AC. </p><p>Level 21: Strength + 8 vs. AC, Constitution + 8 vs. AC, or Dexterity + 8 vs. AC. </p><p><b>Hit:</b> 1d6 + Strength modifier, Constitution modifier, or Dexterity modifier damage, and you knock the target prone. </p><p><b>Effect:</b> After shifting and making this power's attacks, you are stunned until the start of your next turn. </p><p>Published in Dragon Magazine 389. </p>",
